enigma_edit.model

Interface Tileset.Named

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Tileset.Alias, Tileset.Kind, Tileset.Name, Tileset.NamedVariant
    Enclosing class:
    Tileset

    public static interface Tileset.Named
    Interface for named entities, i.e. kinds, named variants and aliases. Each kind has a unique name and optionally several aliases. A variant might have a name. And anything that has a name, may have an additional deprecated name which will be called the oldname.
